name: Princess of Nothing
description:
Simple little F/F fantasy I made in a day to test out RPG Maker MV. Might expand on it, might not. Have fun.

If you're using a mouse/touch controls, you need to open/close the menu using right click. On a phone this should be a long tap or tapping with 2 fingers.

Plugins:

  • Yanfly - Party System, Victory Aftermath, Skill Core
  • Ellye- Simple ATB
